---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Unit" subtitle="Parlier High School NJROTC" disableHero>
<div class="BG555">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h1 class="section-title">About Our Unit</h1>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Leadership Through Service, Excellence Through Commitment</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-card">
            <div class="card-overlay"></div>
            <div class="content-wrapper">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <p class="intro-text">
                        At Parlier High School NJROTC, we believe leadership begins with service to our community, 
                        to our nation, and to one another. Our program is more than a class; it's a family built on 
                        respect, discipline, and teamwork. Every cadet learns that true leadership is measured not 
                        by rank or title, but by the courage to lead with integrity and the commitment to do what 
                        is right, even when no one is watching.
                    </p>
                    
                    <div class="core-values">
                        <h3 class="values-title">Our Core Values</h3>
                        <p class="values-intro">
                            Rooted in the Navy's core values of Honor, Courage, and Commitment, we strive to develop 
                            young men and women who exemplify these principles in their daily lives.
                        </p>
                        
                        <div class="value-item">
                            <div class="value-icon honor">
                                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#e6b220">
                                    <path d="M12 1L3 5v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 9 12 5.16-1.26 9-6.45 9-12V5l-9-4zm0 10.99h7c-.53 4.12-3.28 7.79-7 8.94V12H5V6.3l7-3.11v8.8z"/>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div class="value-details">
                                <h4 class="value-name">Honor</h4>
                                <p class="value-description">Reminds us to live with honesty, respect, and accountability.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="value-item">
                            <div class="value-icon courage">
                                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#e6b220">
                                    <path d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z"/>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div class="value-details">
                                <h4 class="value-name">Courage</h4>
                                <p class="value-description">Drives us to face challenges head on and stand up for what is right.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="value-item">
                            <div class="value-icon commitment">
                                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#e6b220">
                                    <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div class="value-details">
                                <h4 class="value-name">Commitment</h4>
                                <p class="value-description">Inspires us to give our best effort in everything we do in school, at home, and in our community.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <p class="program-text">
                        Through drill, academics, community service, and leadership training, our cadets grow into 
                        confident citizens ready to take on any challenge. We take pride in giving back whether it 
                        is honoring veterans, supporting school events, or mentoring younger students because 
                        community is at the heart of everything we do.
                    </p>
                    
                    <p class="conclusion-text">
                        Together, we lead with purpose, serve with pride, and build a legacy of excellence that 
                        reflects the spirit of Parlier's community that drives Parlier High School and the Navy 
                        tradition we represent.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
    </div>

    <style>
        .BG555 {
            background: #000000;
            color: #fafaf5;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .BG555::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgb(2 60 113 / 40%) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgb(2 60 113 / 40%) 0%, transparent 50%);
            z-index: -1;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
        }
        
        .section-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            padding:6rem 0rem;
        }
        
        .section-title {
            font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif;
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #fafaf5;
            text-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        
        .section-title::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -10px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 100px;
            height: 4px;
            background: #e6b220;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }
        
        .section-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: rgba(250, 250, 245, 0.9);
            max-width: 695px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .content-card {
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
        }
        
        
        .card-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(2, 60, 113, 0.3), rgba(230, 178, 32, 0.1));
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .content-wrapper {
            padding: 3rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        
        .text-content {
            color: #fafaf5;
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        .intro-text {
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .core-values {
            margin: 3rem 0;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: rgba(2, 60, 113, 0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            border-left: 4px solid #e6b220;
        }
        
        .values-title {
            color: #e6b220;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .values-intro {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: rgba(250, 250, 245, 0.9);
        }
        
        .value-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .value-item:hover {
            background: rgba(230, 178, 32, 0.1);
            transform: translateX(5px);
        }
        
        .value-icon {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 1.5rem;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            background: rgba(2, 60, 113, 0.3);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .value-item:hover .value-icon {
            background: rgba(230, 178, 32, 0.2);
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
        
        .value-details {
            flex-grow: 1;
        }
        
        .value-name {
            color: #e6b220;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .value-description {
            color: rgba(250, 250, 245, 0.9);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .program-text, .conclusion-text {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .conclusion-text {
            font-style: italic;
            color: rgba(250, 250, 245, 0.95);
            border-left: 3px solid #e6b220;
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 2.5rem;
        }
        
        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
            }
            
            .section-title {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            
            .section-subtitle {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }
            
            .content-wrapper {
                padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            }
            
            .core-values {
                padding: 1.5rem;
                margin: 2rem 0;
            }
            
            .value-item {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
                padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
            }
            
            .value-icon {
                margin-right: 0;
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .container {
                padding: 2rem 1rem;
            }
            
            .section-title {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .content-wrapper {
                padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
            }
            
            .text-content {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            
            .core-values {
                padding: 1rem;
            }
            
            .values-title {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</div>
</Layout>